reviewText: I loved being in this video - my 6 minutes of fame! What a great gift for children of all ages - great craft ideas! A must have for the holidays!

My 4 year old daughter loves crafts and Disney so when I saw this tape I knew it would be perfect. She watches this over and over ( and its quite long), and can't wait to try some of the ideas for the holidays, we bought it in July! I must admit it is a cute tape and the crafts are definitely child friendly and are done on the tape by the children. This is really holiday family fun.
